        Contents:

        ALLOC          OS/390 assembler code for dynamic
                       allocation
        ALLODEMO       COBOL module showing how to call
                       ALLOC - find COBOL copy area in it
        ASM            JCL to run the assembler
        CONCAT         Dynamic concatenation module
        DDCHCK         DDName checker (see if it's allocated
                       and to whom)
        UNALLOC        Dynamic unallocation routine (Free)

